This folder is for R source files.
Individual functions a are to be stored in functions_src folder.

The functions.R script will read them all.

In the functions src folder : .R 
Riles that start with 0 are functions that do not require other home-made functions.
Files that start with 1 are functions that require 0 functions
Files that start with 2 are functions that require 1 functions 
etc...